latestPosts.caption:
Flew solo to sunny Florida to capture 5 national parks (and their inclusive trails ✨) with my handheld Canon R5. 

Spent 2 days profusely sweating with @sweet.satellite as we drove from park to park, snapping her in front of all the lush accessible scenery. Huge thanks to @accessnowapp and @visitlauderdale for making this possible. Can I come back already 🥹

latestPosts.caption: Step into the world of Mrs. Doubtfire! Watch the transformation process and see her come to life for Halloween 👵🏼🥹 #halloween #mrsdoubtfire #costume #makeuptransformation

taggedUsers.full_name: The Good Stuff with Mary Berg

latestPosts.caption:
HELLOOOOO! Mrs. Freakin’ Doubtfire. I still can’t believe she’s finally come to life! I’ve been imitating her since I was a little boy, getting laughs during recess, and this week I got to fully embody her. 

Huge applause to the magician @samanthacouturemakeup - SFX Makeup Artist that created my prosthetic! Our journey began way back in February with a proper face mould, followed by months of tweaks to get the face, the wig, the outfit and the padding just right. 

What a true joy this has been. Seeing all your faces light up was everything. And a true cherry on top was winning 🥇 best costume at @elconventorico Somewhere, I know Robin Williams is smiling. 

We’re going to be alright poppet. Bye-bye 👵🏼

latestPosts.caption: Celebrating five years of the Neutrogena x Drag Race campaign! This year I had fun focusing on bright, clean, and campy portraits with a beauty dish. Instead of the usual makeup wipe post-removal, I went for an editorial twist, making it look like the makeup was lifted right off the face—shoutout to Hedwig and the Angry Inch for the inspo (check the last slide). Big thanks to the glam squad @viktorpeters @kirstenklontz @alanmoehair, and the legendary @bhytes ✨

latestPosts.caption: MAC wanted 3 high-impact reels of their Pride walk 💄I took inspo from the hectic zooms in Charli XCX’s ‘Von Dutch’ video and also wanted to play with a slow shutter speed to create a dizzying pace. Made a custom track before the shoot by blending stems from 2 different copyright-cleared songs and adding like a dozen sfx (breakdown in last slide) 🌈💋
